    "Furthermore, RL was employed as an alternative approach, incorporating both training and evaluation phases to identify input scenarios that potentially lead to the longest execution times.",
    "The combination of a reward function that emphasizes both execution time and diversity would enable the agent to explore a wide range of scenarios while focusing on the primary objective of WCET estimation.Overall, the methodologies described in this chapter offer a framework for estimating WCET in complex real-time robotic systems.",
